#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wfs.rst:629
msgid "Transaction"
msgstr "Transaction"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wfs.rst:631
msgid ""
"This request allows to update, delete or add one or several features thanks "
"to a XML document. The :ref:`delete <wfs_transaction_delete>` action may be "
"achieved with a POST request as well as with the :ref:`OPERATION "
"<wfs_transaction_operation>` parameter while the :ref:`add "
"<wfs_transaction_add>` and the :ref:`update <wfs_transaction_update>` "
"operations may be achieved through POST request only."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj zahtev omogućava ažuriranje, brisanje ili dodavanje jednog ili više "
"objekata pomoću XML dokumenta. Akcija :ref:`delete <wfs_transaction_delete>`"
" može se izvršiti POST zahtevom, kao i pomoću parametra :ref:`OPERATION "
"<wfs_transaction_operation>`, dok se operacije :ref:`add "
"<wfs_transaction_add>` i :ref:`update <wfs_transaction_update>` mogu "
"izvršiti samo POST zahtevom."

